A cross-platform mobile application built with React Native, powered by a Node.js backend and MongoDB database, designed to streamline hostel operations including room allocation, resident management, complaint handling, payment tracking, and more.

📱 Tech Stack
Frontend: React Native

Backend: Node.js, Express.js

Database: MongoDB (with Mongoose ORM)

Authentication: JWT (JSON Web Tokens)

State Management: Context API / Redux (based on your implementation)

Deployment: Optional — include if hosted (Heroku, Render, Vercel, etc.)

🔑 Features
👨‍💼 Admin
Manage student/resident profiles

Allocate/deallocate rooms

View occupancy status

View and resolve complaints

Generate reports

🧑‍🎓 Student / Resident
Register/login

View room details and allocation

Submit complaints or requests

View payment history and dues

Notifications for important announcements

